sectionText: Restricted to graduate online non-degree, online MCS, online MSME and online MS CE students. Center for Innovation in Teaching & Learning (CITL) restrictions and assessments apply, see http://online.illinois.edu. For more details on this course section, please see http://engineering.illinois.edu/online/courses/. Non-Degree students may enroll on a space-available basis with consent of Program Coordinator, Meg Griffin  (mgriffn@illinois.edu).
